{
  "dialogue": {
    "I don't know you. Why are you talking to me?": ["Mon"],
    "Oh, is it my birthday? I was hoping I'd forget.": [
      "AcceptBirthdayGift_Loved"
    ],
    "This is actually really nice, though. Thank you.": [
      "AcceptBirthdayGift_Loved_sv1"
    ],
    "Oh, is it my birthday? That's right... I almost forgot. Thanks.": [
      "AcceptBirthdayGift_Liked"
    ],
    "I don't have to go into work today, so I'm not complaining...": [
      "GreenRain"
    ],
    "Oh, there's some kind of weird weather today? I didn't notice.": [
      "GreenRain_2"
    ],
    "Heh... thanks. Tastes just like beer.": ["AcceptGift_StardropTea"],
    "Um... sure.": ["FlowerDance_Accept"],
    "I'd better stop eating...": ["FlowerDance_Accept_sv1"],
    "Oh, you made it? *squish*... Um... *smack*... I think I'll stick to frozen pizza. But thanks.": [
      "AcceptGift_203"
    ],
    "Have you tried the new Joja Bubblerito? I ate two in one sitting yesterday, that was a mistake...": [
      "eventSeen_611944_memory_oneweek"
    ],
    "I... wasn't really expecting this, after all I've put you through...": [
      "dating_Shane"
    ],
    "I think I might be the luckiest guy in the world...": [
      "dating_Shane_memory_oneday"
    ],
    "Sorry you had to see me like that, @...": ["eventSeen_3910975"],
    "I'm trying to cut back on the drinks... it's not going to be easy.": [
      "eventSeen_3910975_memory_oneweek"
    ],
    "Buh... hope the bar's open.": ["Resort_Entering"],
    "Welp... got my year's supply of Vitamin D. Now I can play video games with the blinds shut the rest of the year.": [
      "Resort_Leaving"
    ],
    "That's right... I'm not wearing any shoes or socks.": ["Resort_Shore"],
    "Some call it a public health risk.": ["Resort_Shore_sv1"],
    "The crabs seem to enjoy it, though.": ["Resort_Shore_sv2"],
    "Hoo... Feels good to rest these hams.": ["Resort_Chair"],
    "If anyone needs me, I'll just be sitting here, marinating.": [
      "Resort_Chair_sv1"
    ],
    "Phew... feels good to have a cold drink...": ["Resort_Bar"],
    "Or maybe a few...": ["Resort_Bar_sv1"],
    "Okay, this sand is piping hot. I regret not wearing shoes.": ["Resort"],
    "Dance? Hoo-boy. Okay... let me chug a few more of these first...": [
      "FlowerDance_Accept_Spouse"
    ],
    "...No.": ["FlowerDance_Decline"],
    "I heard you built Pam a house... That's really generous...": [
      "pamHouseUpgrade"
    ],
    "You know, I could use a hundred thousand gold myself...": [
      "pamHouseUpgrade_sv1"
    ],
    "*ahem* ...ah ...Just kidding. ...Heh.": ["pamHouseUpgrade_sv2"],
    "I heard someone bought Pam a house... *sigh*... What did Pam ever do to earn that kind of generosity??": [
      "pamHouseUpgradeAnonymous"
    ],
    "...": ["divorced"],
    "...Leave me alone.": ["divorced_sv1"],
    "*gulp* Oh... Yeah, okay... I guess I should've seen this coming.": [
      "breakUp"
    ],
    "I'll... uh... guess I'll see you at the Saloon.": ["breakUp_sv1"],
    "%Shane has a glazed look in his eye. He won't speak to you.": [
      "dumped_Guys"
    ],
    "I don't understand you... *sigh*...": ["secondChance_Guys"],
    "I hardly know you. Why are you talking to me?": ["Mon2_mw"],
    "What's the point of talking to me? I don't want any friends.": [
      "Mon2_mw_sv1"
    ],
    "Hey. Sorry if I came off as rude when we first met.": ["Mon4"],
    "It takes me a while to warm up to strangers.": ["Mon4_sv1_mw1"],
    "It's a lot of effort to be friends with someone. It's easier to just be alone.": [
      "Mon4_sv1_mw2"
    ],
    "I'll be honest, I still can't understand why you'd want to be friends with me.": [
      "Mon6_mw"
    ],
    "Life isn't fair, and I can't help but feel bitter about it.": [
      "Mon6_mw_sv1"
    ],
    "Do you ever feel like the whole world is scrutinizing you like some disgusting insect?": [
      "Mon10"
    ],
    "What? What do you want? Go away.": ["Tue"],
    "What do you want from me? Money? I'd give you a pot of gold to leave me alone!": [
      "Tue2"
    ],
    "Every time I try something new it goes horribly wrong. You learn to just stay in a shell.": [
      "Tue4"
    ],
    "Life isn't so bad... at least I have frozen pizza and eggs.": ["Tue6"],
    "We should go to a Tunnelers game some time. When I go by myself, I usually drink way too much beer.": [
      "Tue8"
    ],
    "I need to keep it together for Jas' sake. I don't want to be a bad role model for her.": [
      "Tue10_mw"
    ],
    "I'm kind of like a father figure to Jas. I just hope I haven't let her down too much.": [
      "Tue10_mw_sv1"
    ],
    "No, I don't have time to chat with you.": ["Wed"],
    "I guess I've grown attached to Marnie and Jas. We're a ragtag bunch but it kind of feels like a weird family.": [
      "Wed8"
    ],
    "I never really had much of a family as a kid.": ["Wed8_sv1"],
    "*sigh* ...Every day is the same. Stocking those horrible shelves, going to the saloon, tossing and turning all night.": [
      "Wed4_prereq_1"
    ],
    "I hated my job at JojaMart, but now that I'm unemployed I feel even worse.": [
      "Wed4_prereq_2"
    ],
    "What do you want? Leave me alone.": ["Thu"],
    "You're really persistent. I guess I'm just surprised that anyone would be interested in talking to me.": [
      "Thu4"
    ],
    "Buh... Where's the Joja Cola?": ["Thu6_mw"],
    "Why try? Life's just a roll of the dice.": ["Thu6_mw_sv1"],
    "When they rolled mine, the dice fell off the table.": ["Thu6_mw_sv2"],
    "You like talking to me? I guess I believe you... maybe you're as weird as I am.": [
      "Thu8"
    ],
    "Don't you have work to do?": ["Fri"],
    "%Shane's hard at work. He doesn't seem interested in talking.": [
      "JojaMart"
    ],
    "What's the point of life if all you do is work?": ["Fri4_prereq_1"],
    "I haven't been able to pay my rent, but Marnie's letting me stay anyway. I'm lucky.": [
      "Fri4_prereq_2"
    ],
    "I'll definitely be going to the saloon tonight. What else is there to do?": [
      "Fri6"
    ],
    "Buh... Can you imagine how disgusting my liver must look?": ["Fri8"],
    "My body feels twenty years older than it should...": ["Fri8_sv1"],
    "My body hurts a lot less since I cut back on the booze.": ["Fri10"],
    "But it still feels like I'm always teetering on the edge...": [
      "Fri10_sv1"
    ],
    "Why are you bothering me? I want to be alone.": ["Sat"],
    "I'm surprised that you're still trying to make friends with me. Haven't I been rude enough to you yet?": [
      "Sat2_chance_1"
    ],
    "*sigh*...": ["Sat2_chance_2"],
    "I'm renting my room from Marnie at a really good price. It's small but I can't complain.": [
      "Sat4_prereq_1"
    ],
    "If I could reset my life maybe I'd start a chicken farm. Only free-range eggs of course.": [
      "Sat4_prereq_2"
    ],
    "I've really grown attached to Marnie's chickens.": ["Sat8_mw"],
    "A chicken will never let you down. Humans, on the other hand...": [
      "Sat8_mw_sv1"
    ],
    "Your farm seems like a great place to raise chickens.": ["Sat10"],
    "I'm busy, can't you tell?": ["Sun_mw"],
    "...I don't feel like talking to anyone.": ["Sun_mw_sv1"],
    "You again? How many times do I have to tell you to leave me alone?": [
      "Sun2"
    ],
    "Hmm... it's %time. Should I throw a frozen pizza in the microwave, or should I wait?": [
      "Sun4_mw"
    ],
    "If the Tunnelers win, I'll knock back a cold one to celebrate.": [
      "Sun4_mw_sv1"
    ],
    "If they lose? I'll have a cold one to drown my sorrows.": ["Sun4_mw_sv2"],
    "...I think I might be gaining weight.": ["Sun6"],
    "If I watch more TV maybe I can forget about life. That would be relaxing.": [
      "Sun8"
    ],
    "Hi, @. I've actually been having a pretty good day so far.": ["Sun10"],
    "Okay... that'll require a great script. Maybe I'll ask Elliott for advice next time I see him at the saloon.": [
      "event_room1"
    ],
    "Sounds great. I'll have to create a bunch of practical effects to make it look cool.": [
      "event_room2"
    ],
    "I didn't know you were such a miser...": ["event_noLoan1"],
    "Okay, Dad...": ["event_noLoan2_male_farmer"],
    "Okay, Mom...": ["event_noLoan2_female_farmer"],
    "Oh, wow...": ["event_noLoan3"],
    "...Yeah, me too.": ["event_apologize1"],
    "I know... that's why I stopped by, to tell you about it.": [
      "event_apologize2"
    ],
    "Wow, it was that serious, huh? I can hardly remember...": [
      "event_apologize3"
    ],
    "Oh yeah? I guess that makes sense.": ["event_stadium1"],
    "Me? I get bored with Pelican Town sometimes.": ["event_stadium1_sv1"],
    "But... I like that you're different. We balance each other out.": [
      "event_stadium1_sv2"
    ],
    "Oh really? I'm surprised... Didn't you move to Stardew Valley to escape the noise of the city?": [
      "event_stadium2"
    ],
    "I mean... Don't get me wrong, I totally understand. My life in Pelican Town is pretty bland, you know.": [
      "event_stadium2_sv1"
    ]
  },

  "marriage_dialogue": {
    "I hope Jas and Marnie are doing alright without me.": ["Rainy_Day_0"],
    "I'm not too worried... Jas is old enough now to take care of the animals on her own.": [
      "Rainy_Day_0_sv1"
    ],
    "You know what? I think I've lost some weight since moving in with you.": [
      "Rainy_Day_1"
    ],
    "Here... take this.": ["Rainy_Day_2"],
    "I bought some of those a while ago and they're almost expired...": [
      "Rainy_Day_2_sv1"
    ],
    "Buhh... I don't feel like being productive today.": ["Rainy_Day_3"],
    "@, should I do something useful today?... or just nap forever?": [
      "Rainy_Day_4"
    ],
    "Hmm... seems like a good night to microwave a few pizza rolls.": [
      "Rainy_Night_0"
    ],
    "Some people like to cook them in the oven, but it just takes too long for me. Plus I like that squishy texture.": [
      "Rainy_Night_0_sv1"
    ],
    "Charlie's doing well.": ["patio_Shane"],
    "The tip-tappa-tip of the rain takes me to a different time... a different place.": [
      "Rainy_Night_1"
    ],
    "I guess... if I had some pants I might've gone outside today... but, nah.": [
      "Rainy_Night_2"
    ],
    "I like gloomy weather, but I feel kinda bad for the hens.": [
      "Rainy_Night_3"
    ],
    "Tip-tappa-tip-tappa-tip... I'm starting to feel thirsty.": [
      "Rainy_Night_4"
    ],
    "Buh... sometimes life feels like a slow, gray blur... know what I mean?": [
      "Indoor_Day_0"
    ],
    "Hey. Take this... I put a bit too much in the microwave.": [
      "Indoor_Day_1"
    ],
    "Sorry if it's squishy.": ["Indoor_Day_1_sv1"],
    "Do me a favor... when I pass away, use my dust to fertilize some corn for the hens.": [
      "Indoor_Day_2"
    ],
    "*smooch*... Mmm, it tastes like someone's been nibbling on pizza rolls.": [
      "Indoor_Day_3"
    ],
    "I may keep to myself a lot, and I may seem unhappy sometimes... but I do appreciate all the work you do. I'm a lucky guy.": [
      "Indoor_Day_4"
    ],
    "I'm just gonna have a couple more beers before closing my eyes for the night.": [
      "Indoor_Night_0"
    ],
    "If... If only... ah, I was just thinking back on the glory days, when I played gridball on the varsity team.": [
      "Indoor_Night_1"
    ],
    "Now I'm old and weak, though...": ["Indoor_Night_1_sv1"],
    "Ughh... *gurgle*... I feel a little bloated... oof... too much Joja all-purpose dipping sauce.": [
      "Indoor_Night_2"
    ],
    "Buh... I wish I was six inches taller and a whole lot smarter...": [
      "Indoor_Night_3"
    ],
    "You like me for who I am? I still have a hard time understanding that...": [
      "Indoor_Night_3_sv1"
    ],
    "I spent all day watching TV and now my legs feel like soft dough. Guess I'll have to take it easy until tomorrow.": [
      "Indoor_Night_4"
    ],
    "I didn't sleep well last night so I'm hoping this fresh air will get the juices flowing.": [
      "Outdoor_0"
    ],
    "What juices, you ask? Heh... you're weird.": ["Outdoor_0_sv1"],
    "Sometimes I stop and realize that I'm nothing more than a bag of juicy, squishy flesh.": [
      "Outdoor_1"
    ],
    "But hey... that's just fine... what's life, anyway?": ["Outdoor_1_sv1"],
    "When I stop and think about it... I'm in a good place. My life is pretty nice.": [
      "Outdoor_2"
    ],
    "Ooohh... my tongue is swollen from eating too many pepper poppers.": [
      "Outdoor_3"
    ],
    "Hey, @. You were sleeping like a baby so I slipped out of bed and went for a morning walk around the farm. Everything looks fine.": [
      "Outdoor_4"
    ],
    "It's weird, when I was younger I swore I'd never have a kid. I wonder what happened to me?": [
      "OneKid_0"
    ],
    "Let's make sure to give %kid1 lots of eggs... Baby's gotta grow those legs!": [
      "OneKid_1"
    ],
    "Papa Shane reporting for duty...": ["OneKid_3"],
    "Buh... I've become corny in my old age.": ["OneKid_3_sv1"],
    "I already fed the kids two bowls of pizza puffs cereal. They'll be full for a while.": [
      "TwoKids_0"
    ],
    "I'll be honest... two kids is enough for me.": ["TwoKids_1"],
    "Ugh... %kid2 is being a little brat today. Must've gotten that from me...": [
      "TwoKids_2"
    ],
    "*Sigh*... If only we could send the kids off to Joja work-camp for a season...": [
      "TwoKids_3"
    ],
    "I'm just kidding.": ["TwoKids_3_sv1"],
    "*Sniff*... *sniff*... mmm... what's that wonderful fragrance you're wearing? Eau de pepperoni?": [
      "Good_0"
    ],
    "You're a lot better-looking than me, you know that?": ["Good_1"],
    "The name 'Shane' means 'Gift from Yoba'... What a joke.": ["Good_2"],
    "I'm in a great mood today... The Tunnelers won big last night.": [
      "Good_3"
    ],
    "Hey, if I ever seem cranky, just ignore it. I get in weird moods sometimes, but it's not about you... okay?": [
      "Good_4"
    ],
    "Ah... life on the farm sure beats working at Joja. That place was disgusting.": [
      "Good_5"
    ],
    "You think it was depressing out front? Kid, you should've seen the back room...": [
      "Good_5_sv1"
    ],
    "Ah... this is the life. No responsibilities, Tunnelers game tonight, fridge stocked with all the goodies a guy could need.": [
      "Good_6"
    ],
    "I don't really feel like doing work today. Maybe I'll see what's on TV.": [
      "Good_8"
    ],
    "Huh... You're wondering why I have this goofy grin on my face? You really have a short memory span, don't you? *blush*": [
      "Good_9"
    ],
    "Oh, do you need something from me? Sorry, I'm kind of busy at the moment.": [
      "Neutral_0"
    ],
    "Why don't you tell me about your day when we're in bed tonight? I'm kind of busy right now...": [
      "Neutral_2"
    ],
    "Working at Joja was a drag, but at least I got to interact with people occasionally.": [
      "Neutral_3"
    ],
    "What, you want me to clean the dishes? I'll do it... eventually...": [
      "Neutral_4"
    ],
    "Are we doing okay on money? I don't want to have to go back to work at Joja.": [
      "Neutral_5"
    ],
    "If you need to go see your friends in town, go ahead. I'm happy in the company of the TV and a couple of tall boys.": [
      "Neutral_6"
    ],
    "Ugh... clean, clean, clean. Sweep, sweep, sweep. Bathe. Cook. Make the bed... Oh, well. Life's alright.": [
      "Neutral_8"
    ],
    "Look, I just want to be alone. Why don't you go outside and do your own thing for a while?": [
      "Bad_5"
    ],
    "What do you want? You sound like Marnie on one of her bad days. Go away.": [
      "Bad_6"
    ],
    "Farm-life is actually really boring. What am I doing here?": ["Bad_7"],
    "Yeah... *hic* ... Sure, honey. Whatever you say... *hic*": ["Bad_8"],
    "I'm going to go out today, alright?": ["funLeave_Shane"],
    "Sorry if I'm sweaty... That was quite a walk... Buh, I'm out of shape.": [
      "funReturn_Shane"
    ],
    "Ooo... my throbbing head. How many did I have last night?": ["spring_1"],
    "The egg festival is probably my favorite... you know how I am, I go crazy for anything to do with chickens.": [
      "spring_12"
    ],
    "Oh, right. It's the flower dance tomorrow. Hey, if it makes you happy, I'm happy.": [
      "spring_23"
    ],
    "I like seeing all the tropical plants this time of year. The valley gets so lush.": [
      "summer_1"
    ],
    "I might fast until the luau tomorrow. I need the ol' bag to be empty so I can fill it with piping hot soup.": [
      "summer_10"
    ],
    "What are your plans for the fall? I'm going to try and incorporate more wine into my diet.": [
      "summer_27"
    ],
    "Hmm... I might have to buy a few cases of pumpkin ale to celebrate the season...": [
      "fall_1"
    ],
    "I'll be helping Marnie with the animals at tomorrow's fair, like usual. You should just kick back and have some fun.": [
      "fall_15"
    ],
    "I'm starting to really feel my age... and I'm not comfortable with that at all.": [
      "fall_17"
    ],
    "Any big plans this winter? I'll probably end up watching a lot of TV and just hanging out around the house.": [
      "winter_1"
    ],
    "Well, another year gone by... I look a little older, but that's about all.": [
      "winter_28"
    ]
  },
  "misc": {
    "If I hadn't met you, @... I might not even be here right now.": [
      "SummitEvent_Dialogue3_Shane"
    ],
    "Which would be a shame, because the bird-watching up here is phenomenal": [
      "SummitEvent_Dialogue3_Shane_sv1"
    ],
    "Heh... I... I tend to joke a lot, because...well…": [
      "SummitEvent_Dialogue3_Shane_sv2"
    ],
    "I guess keeping things light-hearted makes it so I don't have to open up and make myself vulnerable.": [
      "SummitEvent_Dialogue3_Shane_sv3"
    ],
    "But every season that goes by, with you, I get a little more comfortable with myself.": [
      "SummitEvent_Dialogue3_Shane_sv4"
    ],
    "Uh.. I guess what I want to say is…": ["SummitEvent_Dialogue3_Shane_sv5"],
    "I have no regrets marrying you!": ["SummitEvent_Dialogue3_Shane_sv6"],
    "Buh... Yeah, I guess this might be okay. *sniff* *sniff* ... a snack might help.": [
      "Shane_summer_movie_0_BeforeMovie"
    ],
    "I'm rooting for the villain... *urp*": [
      "Shane_summer_movie_0_DuringMovie"
    ],
    "Okay, I'll admit... I thought it was pretty good.": [
      "Shane_summer_movie_0_AfterMovie"
    ],
    "Heh. I'm actually interested in seeing this one...": [
      "Shane_love_BeforeMovie"
    ],
    "Okay, this is good...": ["Shane_love_DuringMovie"],
    "When you're watching a good movie, you can forget about everything else... That's a gift.": [
      "Shane_love_AfterMovie"
    ],
    "Ugh... this is going to be painful.": ["Shane_dislike_BeforeMovie"],
    "Shane's slumped over...": ["Shane_dislike_DuringMovie"],
    "I feel depressed...": ["Shane_dislike_AfterMovie"],
    "The movie theater isn't open on festival days!": ["MovieInvite_Festival"],
    "The movie theater is closed for the night...": ["MovieInvite_Closed"],
    "You're the new farmer, aren't you?": ["WipedMemory"],
    "You seem... no. I'm sure we've never met.": ["WipedMemory_sv1"],
    "Remind me to brush my teeth tonight... there's twelve unique soda flavors, and I'm on track to try them all.": [
      "DesertFestival_Shane_marriage"
    ],
    "Mmm... cave carrot soda... *slurp*": ["DesertFestival_Shane_marriage_sv1"],
    "I came here once when I was a kid... The only thing I remember is getting sick on the bus ride.": [
      "DesertFestival_Shane"
    ],
    "Oh, you want to see a show, huh? Buy me a snack and it's a deal, hehe...": [
      "MovieInvite_Spouse_Shane"
    ],
    "I'll meet you there.": ["MovieInvite_Spouse_Shane_sv1"],
    "Found some food in the freezer. It's yours for cheap. Just don't look at the expiration date.": [
      "Shop_Shane"
    ],
    "Hey, @. I'm your secret gift-giver this year.": ["Event_cs_1499"],
    "Here, open it.": ["Event_cs_1499_sv1"],
    "It's not much, but I hope you like it.": ["Event_cs_1500"],
    "Hi. So, I'm your secret gift-giver this year.": ["Event_cs_1501"],
    "Well? Open it!": ["Event_cs_1501_sv1"],
    "It's nothing fancy, but it's the best I could afford.": ["Event_cs_1504"],
    "Oh! So it's you?": ["Event_cs_1801"],
    "Ah... {1} {0}! Thanks.": ["Event_cs_1801_sv1"],
    "Of course I'll dance with you!": ["Event_cs_1632"],
    "You want to be my partner for the flower dance?": ["Event_cs_1634"],
    "Okay. I look forward to it.": ["Event_cs_1633_sv1"],
    "Okay! I'd love to.": ["Event_cs_1634_sv1"],
    "I'm sorry... I already have a partner.": ["Event_cs_1635"],
    "Yes, dear?": ["Event_cs_1736"],
    "...Yes?": ["Event_cs_1738"],
    "The wedding was wonderful... wasn't it, dear?": ["Game1_cs_2782"],
    "Well, we can't forget about the farm... time to get to work.": [
      "Game1_cs_2782_sv1"
    ],
    "Umm... I don't think so.": ["NPC_cs_3956"],
    "Is this a joke? I don't get it.": ["NPC_cs_3957"],
    "...I don't really know you well enough...": ["NPC_cs_3958"],
    "Uh... This is awkward. Look, I don't really know you that well...": [
      "NPC_cs_3959"
    ],
    "Oh? ...Sorry... I'm not ready for that.": ["NPC_cs_3960"],
    "...I didn't know. Uh... Sorry. No.": ["NPC_cs_3961"],
    "...You want to get more serious? I feel the same way.": ["NPC_cs_3963"],
    "I'm kind of nervous. Aren't you?": ["NPC_cs_3963_sv1"],
    "You just got engaged! What are you thinking?": ["NPC_cs_3965"],
    "What? Didn't you just ask someone else to marry you? You're crazy!": [
      "NPC_cs_3966"
    ],
    "Um, aren't you already married?": ["NPC_cs_3967"],
    "You're already married, you weirdo!": ["NPC_cs_3968"],
    "You're strange.": ["NPC_cs_3970"],
    "Heh. Funny joke.": ["NPC_cs_3971"],
    "Oh!! ...": ["NPC_cs_3972"],
    "@... I'm sorry, but no. I won't marry you right now.": ["NPC_cs_3972_sv1"],
    "!! Er... I'm sorry, I don't feel that way about you...": ["NPC_cs_3973"],
    "Look. I already told you no! Leave me alone.": ["NPC_cs_3974"],
    "You already asked me that. What part of 'NO' don't you understand?!": [
      "NPC_cs_3975"
    ],
    "...!!!": ["NPC_cs_3980"],
    "I accept!!": ["NPC_cs_3980_sv1"],
    "I'll set everything up. We'll have the ceremony in 3 days, okay?": [
      "NPC_cs_3980_sv3"
    ],
    "So...I heard you secretly gave {0} a gift today...": ["NPC_cs_3985"],
    "Do I have to be suspicious of you?": ["NPC_cs_3985_sv1"],
    "Honey... I wanted to give you that fruit as a symbol of my love.": [
      "NPC_cs_4001"
